Reuben M. Manley, Executor, etc., v. Ada M. Osborne et al. Reuben M. Manley, Executor, etc., v. Ada M. Osborne et al. No. 13,333. (75 Pac. 1133.) No. 13,334.

(75 Pac. 1133.)

Error from Atchison district court; W. T. Bland, judge. Opinion filed February 6, 1904. Affirmed. Z. F. Bird, for plaintiff in error. Jackson cfe Jackson, for defendants in error. Per Curiam:

'These are companion cases to Manley v. Mayer, ante, page 377, involving the same questions. For the reasons given in the opinion filed in that case, the same order is made in each of these.
